&lt;p&gt;The Nitro Automate Platform is at the forefront of Nitro’s evolution – powering cutting-edge AI solutions that transform how businesses interact with documents and automate workflows. Our platform includes REST APIs for PDF and document manipulation, no-code workflow automation tools, MCP (Model Context Protocol) servers, and deeply integrated AI capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a unique opportunity to lead an ambitious, high-impact team building the infrastructure that powers the next generation of intelligent document automation.&lt;/p&gt;
